<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.170225>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Ventral view of hind femora representing features of: 1, dark coloured femur; 2, light coloured femur with dark ring; 3, light coloured femur without ring." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/170225/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.170230>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. Known distribution of: Z. angustifasciatum; Z. batesi; Z. dugdalei; Z. kaikouraiensis; Z. minutum; Z. nonmaculatum; Z. taranakiensis; Z. opacum. The Z. batesi record on Kermadec Island is not shown here. (Map with permission from Ian Henderson, Massey University)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/170230/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

